A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Motor Vehicles – Reckless, Negligent, and Aggressive Driving
3 FOR the purpose of altering the penalties and points assessments related to the offenses of
4 reckless, negligent, and aggressive driving; adding certain motor vehicle offenses as
5 elements that may contribute to charges for reckless or aggressive driving; and
6 generally relating to motor vehicle offenses.
